CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 3, 1970, pg. 17, reads: "An Attractive Trio - Three of the attractive young ladies who modeled at the Harriet Tubman Guild's recent 'Winter Fantasy,' are shown above. Members of Letha Hunt's Mona Lisas are from left to right: Marian Henderson, Diane Franklin and Sondria Pettigrew. - Harris photos."
TitMainTitle: Barbara [B.] Smith modeling long sleeveless polka dot one piece outfit and feathered mules, for Harriet Tubman Guild "Winter Fantasy" fashion show
